                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir ewch nehst <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> zu guter mass
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, also <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir auch noch in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen zutun, daz wir wol
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
